page-index-meta-description: Cloiinkcoin bu ụzọ zuru ụwa nile, nke akwadopụtàrà maka ego na ụdịrị ngwa kòmpụtà ọhụrụ. Na Cloiinkcoin, ị nwere ike ide koodù na-achịkwa ego, ma ruo ngwa kòmpụtà ndị enwere ike inweta ebe ọ bụla n’ ụwa.
page-index-sections-developers-desc: Mụta banyere teknuzu dabere na Cloiinkcoin na ngwa kòmpụtà ya ka inwe ike ibido ruwa oru na ya.
page-index-sections-developers-image-alt: Ihe ngosi eji aka arụ Cloiinkcoin glyph nke ejiri lego brik ruo
page-index-sections-enterprise-desc: Hụ otu Cloiinkcoin nwere ike isi mepee ụdị azụmaahịa ọhụụ, belata ọnụahịa gị yana gosipụta azụmaahịa gị n'ọdịnihu.
page-index-sections-enterprise-image-alt: Ihe ngos otu na-arụ ọrụ na arumaru Cloiinkcoin na akuku laptọọpụ
page-index-sections-individuals-desc: Mee ka imara Cloiinkcoin, Ether, akpa ego intaneti, nnochianya ego na ihe ndị ọzọ ka ị wee malite eji ngwa komputa Cloiinkcoin.
page-index-sections-individuals-image-al: Ihe ngosi nkịta doge nọ odu na kòmpụtà
page-index-subtitle: Na Cloiinkcoin, ị nwere ike ide koodu na-achịkwa uru dijitalụ, na aru oru dika esi hazie ya, ma ana enweta ya na ebe obula na ụwa niile.
page-index-title: Cloiinkcoin bụ ebe nweta meghere emeghe nke uwa niile maka nhazighari ngwa komputa.
